      "title": "CSIDH-EKE Public Parameters\nprime p = 4 \\times \\ell_1 \\cdots \\ell_n - 1\nsupersingular curve E_0/\\mathbb{F}_p with order p+1\nAlice\nBob\nKey Generation\nKey Generation\n1. [\\mathfrak{a}] = [\\mathfrak{l}_1^{e_{A1}} \\cdots \\mathfrak{l}_n^{e_{An}}]\n1. [\\mathfrak{b}] = [\\mathfrak{l}_1^{e_{B1}} \\cdots \\mathfrak{l}_n^{e_{Bn}}]\n2. E_A = [\\mathfrak{a}]E_0\n2. E_B = [\\mathfrak{b}]E_0\n3. \\hat{A} = \\mathbf{Enc}_{pw}(E_A)\n3. \\hat{B} = \\mathbf{Enc}_{pw}(E_B)\nSecret Generation\nSecret Generation\n\\begin{array}{l} 1. \\ E_A' = \\mathbf{Enc}_{pw}^{-1}(\\hat{A}) \\\\ 2. \\ E_{BA} = [\\mathfrak{b}] E_A' \\end{array}\n1. E'_B = \\mathbf{Enc}_{pw}^{-1}(\\hat{B})\n2. E_{AB} = [\\mathfrak{a}] E_B^{r}\nEve\nOffline Dictionary Attack\n1. Eve observes \\hat{A}\n2. Eve finds pw' such that\nE'_A = \\mathbf{Enc}_{pw'}^{-1}(\\hat{A}) is supersingular",
